The Barbarian teleport is a magic tablet that can be broken by players to teleport to the Barbarian Outpost, north-east of the Tree Gnome Stronghold.

Players can create this item on the lunar lectern in the ceremonial building on Lunar Isle with a piece of soft clay, 2 law runes, 3 fire runes, and 2 astral runes, as well as level 75 Magic while being on the Lunar spellbook.

A player breaking a teleport tablet

The player does not need to have the relevant Magic level to use the tablet, which shares the same rule with all tablets and the player will not receive any experience, although making the teleport tablet does give 72 experience in Magic.

The '''Barbarian teleport''' is a [[magic tablet]] that can be broken by players to [[Teleportation|teleport]] to the [[Barbarian Outpost]], north-east of the [[Tree Gnome Stronghold]].

Players can create this item on the [[Lectern (Lunar)|lunar lectern]] in the ceremonial building on [[Lunar Isle]] with a piece of [[soft clay]], 2 [[law rune]]s, 3 [[fire rune]]s, and 2 [[astral rune]]s, as well as level 75 [[Magic]] while being on the [[Lunar spellbook]].

[[File:Teleport Tablet.gif|left|thumb|130px|A player breaking a teleport tablet]]
The player '''does not''' need to have the relevant Magic level to use the tablet, which shares the same rule with all tablets and the player will not receive any [[experience]], although making the teleport tablet does give 72 experience in Magic.
